Description:
    Creates Node.js HTTP and WebSocket servers with security baked in

Options:
    Server root directory?
        Choose directory to scaffold server.
    HTTP server port?
        Choose HTTP server port
    WebSocket server port?
        Choose WebSocket server port

Example:
    yo techtonic:web

        This will create:
            package.json: Development packages installed by npm
            Gruntfile.js: Configuration for the task runner
            LICENSE: License file (default is MIT)
